746
00:50:17,347 --> 00:50:19,015
-l'll never...
-Whoo-hoo!

747
00:50:19,099 --> 00:50:20,224
Whoo!

748
00:50:20,434 --> 00:50:22,393
-Whoo!
-(LAUGHS)

749
00:50:43,206 --> 00:50:44,498
-Are you ready?
-Yes.

750
