807
00:55:00,672 --> 00:55:02,881
l wanted you to come after me.

808
00:55:05,010 --> 00:55:07,261
Then you got what you wanted.

809
00:55:07,971 --> 00:55:10,306
Now, you want something else.

810
00:55:37,917 --> 00:55:40,169
