902
01:03:42,068 --> 01:03:43,401
He must be kind.

903
01:03:44,987 --> 01:03:46,613
And brave.

904
01:03:48,199 --> 01:03:51,117
Just a little bit brave. That's all.

905
01:03:54,580 --> 01:03:59,251
