963
01:07:13,529 --> 01:07:14,612
Ugh!

964
01:07:15,865 --> 01:07:18,199
l shouldn't hang about
for Dolly's sake, Joseph.

965
01:07:18,284 --> 01:07:20,118
Why not get Millman to order you a taxi?

966
01:07:20,202 --> 01:07:22,412
